name: Twerk It Miley! ~ Free Celeb Super Running Game + Fun Skating Challenge
name_original: Twerk It Miley! ~ Free Celeb Super Running Game + Fun Skating Challenge
description:
A funny, unique and addictive game to show to your friends. Take Miley on an awesome skateboard dash. Collect foam hands and avoid the pesky paparazzi.

"Cool illustrations and designs that simply look amazing" - 96Apps.com

DOWNLOAD FREE TODAY!

FEATURES
- Funny illustrations and design that look amazing
- Tap the screen to jump over paparazzi and slippery banana skins
- In-app purchases to help you achieve rewards faster if needed
- Game Center Leaderboard

FUN FACTS
- If you achieve a distance score of over 300 you’re better than most average players
- If you achieve a distance score of over 800, you’re better than 90% of players
